WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:08:20.132 --> 00:08:21.901
It's not easy being Rob.

00:08:21.934 --> 00:08:24.336
He said being so handsome
made it difficult

00:08:24.369 --> 00:08:26.605
for him
to find meaningful roles.

00:08:26.638 --> 00:08:28.641
I wanted to ask Brad Pitt
about that,

00:08:28.674 --> 00:08:31.010
but he was too busy acting
in meaningful roles.

00:08:31.043 --> 00:08:32.043
[ Laughter ]

